          "settings": {
            "title": "Why should I choose Shukran Islamic Arts over competition?",
            "text": "<p>Shukran Islamic Arts has proved itself on <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/ShukranIslamicGlass\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/ShukranIslamicGlass\">Etsy</a> with over 21 thousand orders and 4000 positive reviews.<br/>We have 24 hours online experts that can solve your problems.<br/>We reply fast to customization requests and generally make your desire happen.<br/>We have a combined manufacturing system that we dispatch metal and glass decors from the same place.</p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "question-2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I cancel my order?",
            "text": "<p>Sure, if your order has not been shipped just reach out over <a href=\"https://shukranislamicarts.com/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://shukranislamicarts.com/pages/contact\">Contact Us</a> or over <a href=\"https://wa.me/908505323308\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://wa.me/908505323308\">WhatsApp</a> and we can cancel your order.</p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "question-3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you do wholesale?",
            "text": "<p>For over 10 products to the same address we can apply wholesale prices, delivery dates may change for wholesale orders. Check out <a href=\"/pages/wholesale-partnership\" title=\"Wholesale & Partnership\">Whole & Partnership Page</a>.</p>",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
