        "question-4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I get my product personalized?",
            "text": "<p>Generally yes you can. But we have some limitations regarding shipping overcharges. Therefore we have limitation of 45\" wide/long. But if you still want bigger products contact with us.<br/>Color can be personalized as desired, contact us for your personalization requests.</p>",
